{"tid":592082,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係Slash?","createTime":"2018-03-14T03:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T00:20:43.000Z","uid":154054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11eb3777f71cba64d25b30a3dda7ba3be1f10756","tid":592082,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"Slash是甚麼？這一詞源於美國諮詢師、專欄作家Marci Alboher的暢銷書《不能只打一份工︰多重壓力下的職場求生術》，意指年輕人不再滿足於專一職業的工作模式，而選擇有多重職業及身份的生活。這些年輕人會在自我介紹時，以斜槓（/，Slash）來顯示不同職業或身份，如「姓名，職業/職業/職業」，因而稱為斜槓青年。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有多重職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414750f658b11f9e24fae64d64de256047e1793f","tid":592082,"uid":24696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T09:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/175038_245e381625ae307caea26e5c3400581b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F175038_245e381625ae307caea26e5c3400581b.png&h=f76bfb16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4572efc7c3efb281847cc922e0dc599d93438cc1","tid":592082,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T11:03:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d262bfe6863a730494e6b0465e44bdda0e185f67","tid":592082,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T11:04:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa0792744217417b171badc494e5796ee71fccce","tid":592082,"uid":159236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"第一下都係諗結他手"},{"pid":"fc651fd3852982681a2d72af018d9717c1f86450","tid":592082,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa0792744217417b171badc494e5796ee71fccce","tid":592082,"uid":159236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"第一下